  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/tasks/t_start-repl.dita" xtrc="shortdesc:1;23:14">The interactive REPL lets you load a Markdown document and explore
  its structure, test XPath queries, and evaluate rules interactively. Use it
  when writing new rules to confirm your queries return what you expect before
  adding them to a rule set.</shortdesc>

