      See <xref href="../../user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/tasks/t_start-repl.dita" xtrc="xref:1;32:62" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?>Install markdown-validator<?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">Install markdown-validator with pip in a Python virtual environment.   After installation, the <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="codeph:1;24:35">md-validate</codeph> command is available from   your terminal.</desc></xref>.</p>
