      against real documents without modifying the rule set file. Use
      <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/tasks/t_start-repl.dita" xtrc="codeph:1;38:15">md-validate validate</codeph> for production validation.</p>
